{"tid":2490862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CDC：美國已有 7700 萬人完整接種疫苗 有5800人仍中招","createTime":"2021-04-16T02:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T02:51:01.000Z","uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5788818753496ed9d92e5484f8c415b8dc3af49b","tid":2490862,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"週四 (15 日) 美國疾病管制與預防中心 CDC 公布最新數據，美國已有 7700 萬人完整接種新冠疫苗，其中有 5800 人接種疫苗後仍確認新疫肺炎，有 74 人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登 6 日宣布到 4 月 19 日所有美國成年人都應有資格獲得疫苗接種，但施打疫苗並非萬靈丹。<br />\n<br />\n根據 CDC 數據顯示，美國大約有 7700 萬人完整接種新冠疫苗，5800 人接種疫苗後仍確認新疫肺炎，其中 396 人需要住院治療，有 74 人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n目前美國可接受疫苗的人群中，所有已注射疫苗的年齡層都發現感染了疫苗。但是，60 歲以上的人感染率略高，而且大多是女性 65%。<br />\n<br />\n根據 CDC 數據分析，輝瑞疫苗宣稱具 95% 有效性，Moderna 疫苗宣稱有效性為 94%，但美國真實數據顯示，輝瑞和 Moderna 疫苗有效性分別為 91% 和 90%。<br />\n<br />\n嬌生新冠疫苗的有效性為 66%，但美國施打該疫苗的真實數據顯示卻升至 72%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3033fca161287a675eb0476c08de7d23d9526d57","tid":2490862,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4630467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4630467&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=764f25f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4630467</a>"},{"pid":"9aa1a8ccfef097359eaf147fb422e6921d4567fb","tid":2490862,"uid":160662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"5800/77M=幾多???"},{"pid":"5061bc8ab06ffae72a4b3e533c16351e984a657f","tid":2490862,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa1a8ccfef097359eaf147fb422e6921d4567fb","tid":2490862,"uid":160662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"5800/77M=幾多???"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"1%唔夠"},{"pid":"cfb9a91e434a824303b8159acdf58e210640d587","